                  ),
                ),
              ),
              // Title
              Positioned(
                left: 20,
                bottom: 16,
                child: Text(
                  title,
                  style: const TextStyle(
                    color: Colors.white,
                    fontSize: 24,
                    fontWeight: FontWeight.w600,
                    letterSpacing: 0.3,
                    shadows: [
                      Shadow(
